  <summary date="2025-03-11T13:56:16Z" status="Introduced in House">Natural Gas Tax Repeal Act

This bill eliminates a program administered by the Environmental Protection Agency that provides support for reducing methane emissions from the oil and gas sector. It also repeals a charge on methane emissions from&#160;facilities that contain petroleum and natural gas systems and emit 25,000 metric tons or more of greenhouse gases per year.</summary>
